{"tid":105474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估國家] 6歲妹踎馬路小便被輾死","createTime":"2017-02-03T02:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T06:42:09.000Z","uid":1251,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f065e7a6544711ffc8bcedb6bbf616cdf144690","tid":105474,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:23:18.000Z","msg":"江西贛州周二（1月31日）發生一宗巴士輾死女童慘劇。當日下午2時33分左右，一名6歲女童獨自走到馬路上蹲下小便，遭一輛停站接載客人的巴士輾壓，途人發現後，趕忙將她從巴士底抱出送院，惜女童最終傷重不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，當時巴士司機因見路邊有2名客人揮手示意要上車，便打算停靠路旁，未料卻輾過了蹲着小便的女童，她被送到鄉衞生院後身亡。目前，巴士司機已因涉嫌交通肇事被刑拘。<br />\n<br />\n女童被輾壓的全程被附近閉路電視拍下，畫面曝光後，引來網民熱議，有人驚呼：「太恐怖了，希望小女孩安息！」但更多人則認為是女童的家長，沒有妥善照顧女童才致釀成悲劇：「父母呢......為甚麼在路邊？撒尿？哎，小孩子的父母也有責任！」「監戶人到哪裡去了？孩子為甚麼要在公路上小便？」<br />\n<br />\n有片 ： <a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170203&amp;guid=56254064&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170203%26guid%3D56254064%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e5242354\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170203%26guid%3D56254064%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=f881cd50\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170203&amp;guid=56254064&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"ebca0ba0e0d7846702d3fbb266b3c44d5c211ffe","tid":105474,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:26:40.000Z","msg":"小孩子都是這樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc1faf906b04c805fc3f1eea3566ed67cafbe6c","tid":105474,"uid":15305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小孩子都是這樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽到呢句就火滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\